data.description: Beautiful home in the guard gated coveted Pace Island community. This well-maintained home features 12 ft ceilings with immense columns in the foyer leading to an open floor plan. Wood floors throughout. Built in entertainment center with bookcases, fireplace and wet bar in the great room. Relax in the air-conditioned sunroom with a peaceful view of the manicured back yard and lake.
